  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: If user denies access to camera on Choose Recipient screen then next time this screen is opened app crashes.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\napp does not crash. User can't use Scan QR functionality (maybe some placeholder is shown instead of camera picture) but can use the rest of features (select fro contact, paste ..)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\napp crashes\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status first time\r\n- Create password\r\n- Open wallet\r\n- Tap Send\r\n- Tap on Recipient field \r\n- Deny access to camera on Choose Recipient screen\r\n- close Choose Recipient screen\r\n- Tap on Recipient field again -> app crashes\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop  0.9.11d179 \r\n* Operating System: \r\nReal device iPhone 6s, iOs 10.3.1\r\nReal device iPhone 7 plus, iOs 11.0.2\r\n",
